results.name: Molien series for invariants of finite Coxeter group A_8.
comment: The Molien series for the finite Coxeter group of type A_k (k >= 1) has G.f. = 1/Prod_{i=2..k+1} (1-x^i).
Note that this is the root system A_k not the alternating group Alt_k.
reference: J. E. Humphreys, Reflection Groups and Coxeter Groups, Cambridge, 1990. See Table 3.1, page 59.
link: Ray Chandler, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000
Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients, signature (0,1,1,1,0,0,-1,-1,-1,-2,-2,0,1,2,3,3,2,1,0,-2,-3,-4,-3,-2,0,1,2,3,3,2,1,0,-2,-2,-1,-1,-1,0,0,1,1,1,0,-1).
maple: seq(coeff(series( mul(1/(1-x^j), j=2..9), x, n+1), x, n), n = 0..70); # _G. C. Greubel_, Feb 01 2020
program: (PARI) Vec( prod(j=2,9, 1/(1-x^j)) + O('x^70) ) \\ _G. C. Greubel_, Feb 01 2020
(MAGMA) R<x>:=PowerSeriesRing(Integers(), 70); Coefficients(R!( (&*[1/(1-x^j): j in [2..9]]) )); // _G. C. Greubel_, Feb 01 2020
return P( product(1/(1-x^j) for j in (2..9)) ).list()
xref: Molien series for finite Coxeter groups A_1 through A_12 are A059841, A103221, A266755, A008667, A037145, A001996, and A266776-A266781.
